		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Can anyone test FDS Metroid on their Hi-Def NES?  Apparently the most recent update to the Analogue Nt Mini, also designed by Kevtris using his FPGA design, may have silenced the door opening sound.  Kevtris asked about it on the AtariAge page dedicated to the Nt Mini.  The firmware upgrade fixed the FDS sound in Bio Miracle Bokutte Upa, but there may be a regression somewhere.<br /><br />Here is the report : <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://atariage.com/forums/topic/242970-fpga-based-videogame-system/?p=3755991">http://atariage.com/forums/topic/242970 ... ?p=3755991</a><!-- m -->

		

